## 3. SEO Implementation (Refactored)
We moved away from `react-helmet-async` to solve SSR/Prerender conflicts on Windows.
- **Native Meta:** Every route uses the React Router [meta](file:///c:/Users/dgper/Proyectos/ZeroCode/apps/reformas/app/routes/contacto.tsx#5-11) export for baked-in SEO.
- **Schema:** [SchemaLocalBusiness](file:///c:/Users/dgper/Proyectos/ZeroCode/apps/reformas/src/core/seo/SchemaLocalBusiness.tsx#13-50) and [SchemaFAQ](file:///c:/Users/dgper/Proyectos/ZeroCode/apps/reformas/src/core/seo/SchemaFAQ.tsx#10-31) now rendered via standard JSON-LD script tags.
- **SSG:** Fully configured via [react-router.config.ts](file:///c:/Users/dgper/Proyectos/ZeroCode/apps/reformas/react-router.config.ts).

