## 5. Firebase Deployment (Fixing EPERM)
We identified an `EPERM` error in your logs:
> `Error: EPERM, Permission denied: ...\dataconnect-emulator-3.1.4.exe`

**Solution:**
1. **Close all Firebase terminals.**
2. **Delete the emulator cache:**
   `rm -Recurse -Force C:\Users\dgper\.cache\firebase\emulators`
3. **Deploy again:**
   `firebase deploy --only hosting:reformas`

